    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>ANNIHILATION APPROACHES</strong>   <br>  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras/6ed1d1f3850c101d3d8125ab5c4fdc05.avif?t=1768517951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras_big/6ed1d1f3850c101d3d8125ab5c4fdc05.avif?t=1768517951 width=800 height=258 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shattered Sun</strong> is a twin-stick action roguelike where time is the ultimate enemy. Pilot a powerful experimental mech and fight your way across the solar system's planets, crushing enemies in your path as you try to escape the unstable sun before it's too late. Do you have what it takes, Commander?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><strong>CUSTOMISE YOUR MECH</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras/69ca79645fffec51e556f2edfce1cb94.avif?t=1768517951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras_big/69ca79645fffec51e556f2edfce1cb94.avif?t=1768517951 width=800 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and equip a vast array of weaponry and armour to experiment with various playstyles and find your preferred way of delivering destruction. Bring the pain with dual miniguns, or get more personal with  flamethrowers. Gracefully weave between enemy attacks with streamlined armour, or become an unstoppable combat force with heavy armour. Discover Cells that modify your weapons in unique ways.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br> <strong>FIGHT AND EXPLORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras/82fe5091787a5b1c64df68e7fe415d46.avif?t=1768517951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras_big/82fe5091787a5b1c64df68e7fe415d46.avif?t=1768517951 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make tactical decisions and plan your route of carnage through the planetary map. Different enemy factions and biomes present unique challenges you must be ready to face, requiring vastly different strategies and equipment to effectively destroy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br> <strong>THE ROGUELIKES YOU LOVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras/c1d81b30d82083d03f5db5f6cb851339.avif?t=1768517951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras_big/c1d81b30d82083d03f5db5f6cb851339.avif?t=1768517951 width=800 height=465 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > With randomly generated planets, a tactical planetary map, and random item drops, no two runs will feel the same. Find new ways to play and constantly hone your skills to endure any challenge the game throws at you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DISCLAIMER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shattered Sun is currently in Alpha. Expect more weapons, armours, abilities, enemies, biomes, cells, and an improved gameplay experience in the near future. Join our public <strong>Discord</strong> server for feedback, FAQs, and information about future content and updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras/3c6c00a314e4ffa70c1b06bb4af084b7.poster.avif?t=1768517951\" width=698 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245300/extras/3c6c00a314e4ffa70c1b06bb4af084b7.mp4?t=1768517951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
